<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:10:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>疑似鳄鱼袭击后失踪12岁儿童遗体被发现</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/remains-of-missing-12-year-old-child-found-after-suspected-crocodile-attack/articleshow/111475457.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111475457.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;澳大利亚警方在帕伦帕 (Palumpa) 的芒果溪 (Mango Creek) 度假期间发现了一名 12 岁儿童被鳄鱼袭击的遗体。高级警官埃里卡·吉布森表达了悲伤。看到一条黑色鳄鱼。北领地有超过 100,000 条鳄鱼。 2013年的一起事件涉及一条4.5米长的鳄鱼； 2017 年，一名男子在一次非致命袭击中幸存。最近，一条凶猛的鳄鱼被射杀、煮熟并吃掉。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 05:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/remains-of-missing-12-year-old-child-found-after-suspected-crocodile-attack/articleshow/111475457.cms</guid></item><item><title>两指测试：巴基斯坦医生因对强奸受害者进行禁止的处女测试而被解雇</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/two-finger-test-doctor-in-pakistan-fired-for-performing-banned-virginity-test-on-rape-victim/articleshow/111476539.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111476539.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 2020 年，大型强子对撞机禁止在强奸检查中使用两指贞操测试，认为它“没有法医价值，是一种耻辱”。​</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 05:34:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/two-finger-test-doctor-in-pakistan-fired-for-performing-banned-virginity-test-on-rape-victim/articleshow/111476539.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着气候变化加剧，中国警告将出现更热、更长时间的热浪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-warns-of-hotter-longer-heatwaves-as-climate-change-intensifies/articleshow/111477446.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111477446.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国的气候正在迅速变化，导致夏季更热、降雨量更大、气温创历史新高。中国气象局警告气温大幅上升和天气模式更加不可预测。该国面临着适应这些变化的挑战，未来可能会出现更多极端高温事件和降雨量增加。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 05:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-warns-of-hotter-longer-heatwaves-as-climate-change-intensifies/articleshow/111477446.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普保持低调，而乔·拜登因候选资格而面临愤怒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-keeps-low-profile-while-joe-biden-faces-furor-over-candidacy/articleshow/111473647.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111473647.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在乔·拜登总统辩论表现不佳后，前总统唐纳德·特朗普战略性地减少了公开露面，让民主党的斗争占据了新闻周期的主导地位。通过避免成为聚光灯并取消计划中的活动，特朗普允许拜登承受更大的政治压力，这导致民意调查显示特朗普在全国和摇摆州的领先优势有所增加。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 03:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-keeps-low-profile-while-joe-biden-faces-furor-over-candidacy/articleshow/111473647.cms</guid></item><item><title>格拉布斯火灾：北加州与多场山火作斗争，26,000 人被疏散</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/grubbs-fire-northern-california-battles-multiple-wildfires-26000-evacuated/articleshow/111472841.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111472841.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴勒莫格拉布斯火灾的疏散令已降级为警告，影响了巴特县的几个地区。这场大火是在格拉布斯路 (Grubbs Road) 和布罗利尔路 (Brollier Way) 附近发生的，是北加州一系列野火的一部分，迫使 26,000 人撤离。奥罗维尔附近的汤普森大火大幅蔓延，同时出现了新的火灾，促使人们进一步疏散。已宣布进入紧急状态，并批准联邦资金支持极端高温和火灾风险下的消防工作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:03:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/grubbs-fire-northern-california-battles-multiple-wildfires-26000-evacuated/articleshow/111472841.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我们都在寻找获胜之路”：20多位州长在拜登下台的呼声中出手相救</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/we-are-all-looking-for-path-to-win-over-20-governors-come-to-bidens-rescue-amid-calls-for-stepping-down/articleshow/111473016.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111473016.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在民主党人对拜登的策略表示怀疑的情况下，白宫新闻秘书让-皮埃尔肯定了拜登对竞选活动的奉献精神。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/we-are-all-looking-for-path-to-win-over-20-governors-come-to-bidens-rescue-amid-calls-for-stepping-down/articleshow/111473016.cms</guid></item><item><title>男子因携带 6 英寸任天堂标志性剑复制品被判入狱</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nuneaton-man-gets-4-months-jail-for-carrying-a-6-inch-toy-sword/articleshow/111473400.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111473400.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;沃里克郡纽尼顿的一名男子安东尼·布雷因携带任天堂《塞尔达传说》系列的 6 英寸大师剑复制品而被判处四个月监禁。尽管他声称这是一个坐立不安的玩具，但他还是因携带带刀片的物品而被捕。布雷被判处四个月监禁，并缴纳 154 英镑的受害者附加费。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nuneaton-man-gets-4-months-jail-for-carrying-a-6-inch-toy-sword/articleshow/111473400.cms</guid></item><item><title>“第二次美国革命如果......”：右翼智库负责人表示他们正在“夺回国家”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/second-american-revolution-if-right-wing-think-tank-head-says-they-are-in-the-process-of-taking-country-back/articleshow/111473578.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111473578.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:48:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/second-american-revolution-if-right-wing-think-tank-head-says-they-are-in-the-process-of-taking-country-back/articleshow/111473578.cms</guid></item><item><title>飓风贝里尔袭击牙买加，带来强风和强降雨</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hurricane-beryl-strikes-jamaica-with-intense-winds-and-heavy-rainfall/articleshow/111472984.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111472984.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周三晚间，4 级飓风“贝丽尔”横扫牙买加，带来强风和强降雨。这场风暴此前曾在加勒比海东南部造成严重破坏并夺去了至少七人的生命。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:08:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hurricane-beryl-strikes-jamaica-with-intense-winds-and-heavy-rainfall/articleshow/111472984.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国总统乔·拜登承认挽救候选人资格的“关键日子”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-president-joe-biden-acknowledges-critical-days-to-save-candidacy/articleshow/111472766.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111472766.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统乔·拜登在辩论表现不佳后承认未来几天对其连任竞选的重要性。尽管来自盟友和捐助者的压力要求他下台，但他仍然决心留在竞选中。拜登计划通过即将到来的露面和采访来安抚选民，同时内部也担心他的生存能力和年龄。一项新的民意调查显示，特朗普在可能选民中领先拜登 6 个百分点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:08:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-president-joe-biden-acknowledges-critical-days-to-save-candidacy/articleshow/111472766.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么穆斯林对极右翼在法国民意调查中获胜持谨慎态度</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/marine-le-pen-national-rally-nr-muslims-france-elections-macron/articleshow/111437345.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111437345.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙对提前选举的赌博适得其反后，马琳·勒庞的注册护士在周日的第一轮投票中遥遥领先，导致他的中间派阵营仅排名第三，落后于注册护士和仓促组建的左翼联盟。民意调查者计算出，第一轮选举中，RN 有望获得 250-300 个席位。但那是在战术性撤退和跨党派呼吁选民支持最有可能击败当地共和党竞争对手的候选人之前。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:41:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/marine-le-pen-national-rally-nr-muslims-france-elections-macron/articleshow/111437345.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯表示已发出停止以色列战争的新“想法”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-says-it-has-sent-new-ideas-on-halting-israel-war/articleshow/111468152.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111468152.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 19:47:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-says-it-has-sent-new-ideas-on-halting-israel-war/articleshow/111468152.cms</guid></item><item><title>“如果拜登醒了”：白宫简报会变成了关于总统寒冷的午睡时间的辩论。手表</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/if-biden-is-awake-white-house-briefing-turns-into-debate-on-presidents-cold-nap-time-watch/articleshow/111467969.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111467969.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周三，在白宫新闻发布会上，白宫新闻秘书卡琳·让-皮埃尔 (Karine Jean-Pierre) 在白宫新闻发布会上问记者：“你感冒过吗？”总统在这场辩论中表现得摇摇欲坠，这场辩论被归咎于他的感冒，但第二天就恢复了健康。竞选活动。白宫表示，他们在辩论前没有透露有关感冒的信息，因为他们不想使用它。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 19:23:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/if-biden-is-awake-white-house-briefing-turns-into-debate-on-presidents-cold-nap-time-watch/articleshow/111467969.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登和卡玛拉·哈里斯罕见联合露面，在门票存疑中鼓舞士气</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-kamala-harris-joint-rare-appearance-pep-talk-amid-doubt-over-ticket/articleshow/111467204.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111467204.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登与卡马拉·哈里斯和一群有影响力的民主党州长召开了会议，外界猜测他可能会宣布退出连任竞选。但这次会议就像一次鼓舞士气的演讲，确认卡马拉·哈里斯不会取代拜登的位置，拜登也不会考虑选择退出。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:55:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-kamala-harris-joint-rare-appearance-pep-talk-amid-doubt-over-ticket/articleshow/111467204.cms</guid></item><item><title>维韦克·拉马斯瓦米 (Vivek Ramaswamy) 向民主党人提出了“选择哪个傀儡”的建议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/vivek-ramaswamy-has-this-advice-for-democrats-on-which-puppet-to-choose/articleshow/111466690.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111466690.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;被视为共和党副总统候选人的维韦克·拉马斯瓦米(Vivek Ramaswamy)向民主党提出了一条戏谑的建议，因为人们对拜登的替代方案的猜测甚嚣尘上。这位印裔美国亿万富翁表示，民主党越拖延选择他们的“傀儡”，对他们来说就越有利——这与普遍的看法相反，因为在选出新候选人后将会有一个蜜月期。维韦克·拉马斯瓦米表示，民主党的理想情况是在蜜月期间举行没有公众监督的选举。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:10:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/vivek-ramaswamy-has-this-advice-for-democrats-on-which-puppet-to-choose/articleshow/111466690.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登告诉盟友他可能无法挽救候选资格：报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-told-alley-he-may-not-be-able-to-salvage-candidacy-report/articleshow/111465132.cms</link><description>尽管民主党高层在辩论失败后公开表现出勇敢的一面，但总统乔·拜登知道，如果他在未来几天不能让公众相信他知道如何做好这项工作，他可能无法挽救自己的候选资格。据《纽约时报》报道，他已将此事告诉了一位重要盟友。报道称，白宫发言人安德鲁·贝茨驳斥了拜登考虑退出竞选的报道，并表示这“绝对是假的”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:55:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-told-alley-he-may-not-be-able-to-salvage-candidacy-report/articleshow/111465132.cms</guid></item><item><title>“2005年与梅拉尼娅结婚之前”：新文件对特朗普-爱泼斯坦的描述</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/before-marrying-melania-in-2005-what-new-documents-claim-about-trump-epstein/articleshow/111465121.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111465121.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;迄今为止尚未公布的新文件称，唐纳德·特朗普和杰弗里·爱泼斯坦的关系比人们想象的更为亲密。文字记录显示，特朗普在 2004 年至 2006 年间多次给爱泼斯坦打电话。这些屏幕截图于 2008 年被密封，作为亚历山大·阿科斯塔与杰弗里·爱泼斯坦交易的一部分，并于 7 月 1 日发布。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 14:55:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/before-marrying-melania-in-2005-what-new-documents-claim-about-trump-epstein/articleshow/111465121.cms</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示米歇尔·奥巴马领先唐纳德·特朗普，引发了民主党对乔·拜登担忧的猜测</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/polls-show-michelle-obama-leading-donald-trump-sparking-democratic-speculation-amid-joe-biden-concerns/articleshow/111465547.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111465547.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;令人惊讶的是，米歇尔·奥巴马 (Michelle Obama) 成为唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的有力竞争者，在最近的民意调查中以大幅优势领先。民主党主要人物对乔·拜登的表现表示担忧，促使人们呼吁采取紧急行动评估他的候选资格。其他潜在候选人的民意调查结果显示，特朗普的支持率较低，凸显了奥巴马在政治格局中的实力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 16:09:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/polls-show-michelle-obama-leading-donald-trump-sparking-democratic-speculation-amid-joe-biden-concerns/articleshow/111465547.cms</guid></item><item><title>加拿大首次任命女性担任陆军参谋长</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canada-appoints-woman-army-chief-for-first-time-in-countrys-history/articleshow/111464411.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111464411.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 14:19:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/canada-appoints-woman-army-chief-for-first-time-in-countrys-history/articleshow/111464411.cms</guid></item><item><title>认识受《薄伽梵歌》启发的英国印度教保守党候选人雷瓦·古迪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/meet-uks-hindu-conservative-candidate-reva-gudi-who-is-inspired-by-bhagavad-gita/articleshow/111464013.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111464013.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;雷瓦·古迪博士来自费尔特姆和赫斯顿，她说，她受到《薄伽梵歌》中超然的信息的启发。这位印度教候选人表示，吉塔的信息帮助她在男性主导的政治世界中找到了方向，她是在担任 NHS 全科医生 20 多年后进入这个世界的。 “作为一名印度教女性，我有时确实面临着独特的挑战，包括克服刻板印象并确保我的声音在男性主导的领域被听到，”她说。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/meet-uks-hindu-conservative-candidate-reva-gudi-who-is-inspired-by-bhagavad-gita/articleshow/111464013.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>